{"tid":1563513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：政府增加房屋供應嘅措施只會陸續有來，絶不走數。","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T13:02:09.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1d35d13974e0048f42dd06a2a7a14dd8139db893","tid":1563513,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:12:34.000Z","msg":"隨著政府將實施空置稅嘅條例草案喺憲報刊登，我舊年六月底公布嘅6項房屋政策新措施已經全部到位，其他5項分别係：<br />\n(1) 將居屋、綠置居同埋「首置」嘅售價同市場樓價脱鈎；<br />\n(2) 將9幅私樓地改撥做公營房屋；<br />\n(3) 市建局出售第一個「首置」項目；<br />\n(4) 運房局成立過渡性房屋專責小組，加快推進各個項目；<br />\n(5) 改善「樓花」預售，防止發展商「唧牙膏」賣樓。<br />\n<br />\n當然，空置稅嘅法案仍須立法會審議通過。房屋係民生頭等大事，政府增加房屋供應嘅措施只會陸續有來，絶不走數。<br />\n<br />\n#房屋政策新措施 #空置稅 #林鄭月娥 #CarrieLam<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/do3i7dF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdo3i7dF.jpg&h=c530754b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/carrielam.hksar/photos/a.745574808955421/1262138827299014/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcarrielam.hksar%2Fphotos%2Fa.745574808955421%2F1262138827299014%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=89c01ff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/carrielam.hksar/photos/a.745574808955421/1262138827299014/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"df9b0a0c0dcfa3a4b12914b2ebeef47f93e9f8e2","tid":1563513,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:13:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.