:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:30:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">對準政權 遍地開花</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2D3bRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2D3bRU.jpg&h=49b546b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXuufm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXuufm1.jpg&h=98681984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yM2WNBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyM2WNBw.jpg&h=9433ed2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zasf29R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzasf29R.jpg&h=aca10195&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc05f297750ec64fbf0c71d1774f6e460b5d2d25","tid":1563513,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"That it's too late to apologize<br />\nIt's too late<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb651e979c5e7d56b1bf270fa693906a91f0b5d1","tid":1563513,"uid":53959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"潛台詞；盡快增加房屋俾新移民"},{"pid":"6fce1cdd5adc56586a127ad14991e4be1556c9f8","tid":1563513,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:33:32.000Z","msg":"【綠置居】景泰苑業主6折168萬買1房單位 持貨不足3年放盤賺145萬<br />\n 17:08 2019/09/09<br />\n<br />\n全港首個綠置居的新蒲崗景泰苑，兩年前以6折發售，入場費僅94萬，超額認購約17.7倍。不過，有業主持貨不足3年，最近在綠表二手市場放盤，其中一個中層293方呎單位，業主當年以168.1萬買入，近日以348萬(綠表、未補地價)沽出，扣除樓價10%額外印花稅(SSD) 約34.8萬元後，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>賬面仍獲利約145.2萬元離場。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n世紀21富山地產聯席董事林偉雄表示，該行新近錄得新蒲崗景泰苑成交，單位為中層12室，實用面積293平方呎，1房2廳間隔，座向東南望開揚景，放盤3星期，原開價360萬元，經議價後以348萬(綠表價)沽出，實用面積呎價11,877元。<br />\n <br />\n據了解，原業主於2017年以168萬元(未補地價) 購入上址，持貨不足3年沽售，扣除樓價10%額外印花稅(SSD) 約34.8萬元後，賬面仍獲利約145.2萬元離場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街離地政府,  自己睇撚清楚 <br />\n屌你老母搞埋啲濕鳩綠置居畀公屋友炒樓<br />\n屌你老母臭閪   真正要住嗰班就幫唔撚到<br />\n幫撚哂啲仆街公屋撚換樓炒樓"},{"pid":"c8f37d9c838db55f1ae0dbee53fbbeb905ad62d8","tid":1563513,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"150個"},{"pid":"ddee59d66a8ed1fb6f11ff518d8ff2e47480ecaa","tid":1563513,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"一手樓空置稅<br />\n有閪用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}